 &lt;div id="van-life-starter-checklist" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#van-life-starter-checklist" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are new, do these in order:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose a reliable van and reserve a maintenance buffer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build only essentials first: sleep, airflow, basic power, basic cooking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pick a simple power path: portable station now or full DIY later.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test your routine for 30 days before buying comfort upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use reviews with real tradeoffs, not just feature lists.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

